==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unglue
<hw>Un*glue"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>glue</ets>.]</ety> <def>To separate, part, or
open, as anything fastened with glue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She stretches, gapes, <qex>unglues</qex> her eyes,⟦br⟧
And asks if it be time to rise.</q> <rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ungod</ent>⟦br⟧
